 paper includes science examples of the\npower of the discovery approach, encompassing all the areas of astrophysics\ncovered by the 2020 Decadal Survey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Mar 2019 16:20:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Mar 2019 12:59:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-19"}
