ed with their\nhost haloes. This suggests that many of the same physical processes determine\nboth the galaxy--filament and the galaxy--halo alignments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Mar 2019 18:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-12"}
